WHAT IS IT?

  "Cubuc" is a Workbench game in which you have to rotate and line
up cubic shapes of 4 different colours, so at least 4 of them line
up in the same direction. The more there are cubes that are lined
up, the more points you get. If all lined up cubes are of the same
colour, you get much more points.

  Each time you rotate a cube and it does not create an alignment
of at least 4 cubes lined up in the same direction, one more cube
will appear on the game board. Just beware that the game board
does not fill up completely, if that happens, the game will end.

  Have fun!

FEATURES

  -There's no complex installation: just run the game and play!

  -The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
   resizeable.

